default7. The statistics relating to the different groups of those who 
defaultare disadvantaged
default tend to be taken separately rather than aggregated.. Thus school students, people with disabilities, college and training studen
defaultts are calculated and generally only provided for (where provision 
defaultisdefault made) as individual minorities, rather than being grouped into a stronger total, reflecting the nature of rural communities and which could well command a stronger place in the market.
default&#xa0;
defaultWe suggest there is a role for a requirement that Local Authorities look to their statutory requirements in the round rather than within separate "s
defaultilo
default" areas.
